                                   Install                                      
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

• Build libpantheon

  bzr branch lp:libpantheon
  cd libpantheon
  mkdir build; cd build
  cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
  make
  sudo make install

• Bugs

  If you find bugs in this installation guide or in libpantheon itself, please report them at
  https://launchpad.net/libpantheon/+filebug


